Fleets may be used to destroy land-based units, including garrisons, on a system where no enemy fleet is located.  To order an orbital bombardment, move a fleet to the system you wish to bombard; once the fleet has arrived at the chosen system, right-click on the fleet, and select 'Orbital Bombardment' from the pop-up menu.  There are three types of orbital bombardments available to us: General, Military, and Civilian; be aware, however, that system loyalty may shift in the Rebel's favor if we destroy non-military targets.